          "reviewBody": "I have studied here fro class nursery to 10th , I can't explain how good this school is .\nSuperb management.\nProper labs .\nRegular health checkup of students as well as teachers .\nDr. nilima prakash ma'am and mis Renu ma'am are the best principles I had ever seen .\nIn many others school I had seen many discrimination between students who are son/daughter of teachers and Normal students but in this school we can't even see it one time not even an single teacher do discrimination even when I was in 10th class my class incharge also have an daughter in our school in same class but she never did any difference between her and rest of class. She treated all the students of our class as her daughter's and son's",
